{"id":23662,"date":"2021-06-10T16:16:12","date_gmt":"2021-06-10T14:16:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/?page_id=23662"},"modified":"2025-01-13T14:08:38","modified_gmt":"2025-01-13T13:08:38","slug":"study-for-life","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/en\/career\/student-opportunities\/study-for-life\/","title":{"rendered":"Study for Life"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"preamble\">Study for Life is a study and mentoring programme for those who have just finished their first year of high school\/gymnasium. We understand that the road to university can feel long \u2013perhaps even more so for those whose families do not have an academic background or have studied elsewhere than Sweden. Our goal is to make the road feel shorter.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-26129 alignnone\" src=\"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/11\/01-corporate-msa-gbg-607-1200x800.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/11\/01-corporate-msa-gbg-607-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/11\/01-corporate-msa-gbg-607-2000x1334.jpg 2000w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/11\/01-corporate-msa-gbg-607-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/11\/01-corporate-msa-gbg-607-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/11\/01-corporate-msa-gbg-607-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/11\/01-corporate-msa-gbg-607-2048x1366.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Each participant in Study for Life will have two mentors to provide support and follow their development throughout the programme. Participants will also have the opportunity to take part in study visits and inspirational lectures and to develop practical skills such as presentation giving either at the firm or one of the companies we work with.<\/p>\n<p>More details and contact information can be found <a href=\"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2024\/04\/MSA_Studera_for_livet_2024_Digital.pdf\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>The application period for next year&#8217;s programme is 1 September \u2013 30 September 2025.<\/p>\n<p>We look forward to meeting future lawyers, doctors, economists, engineers or any other profession of choice!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Study for Life is a study and mentoring programme for those who have just finished their first year of high school\/gymnasium. We understand that the\u2026<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":10,"featured_media":0,"parent":13552,"menu_order":5,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-23662","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"lang":"en","translations":{"en":23662,"sv":18530},"pll_sync_post":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/23662"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/10"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=23662"}],"version-history":[{"count":11,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/23662\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":29432,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/23662\/revisions\/29432"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/13552"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\